## Frontend (React/Vite)
- Framework: React 19 (SPA) + Vite.
- Language: TypeScript (Strict Mode).
- UI Library: ShadcnUI + Tailwind CSS (Lucide Icons).
- State Architecture: Context-based global state (e.g., AuthContext).
